MythRip should run on any machine which meets the following
dependencies:

  * Python 2.6 
  * wxWidgets 2.6 or greater 
  * MythTV bindings 0.24 (libmyth-python)
  * mythtranscode (mythtv-transcode-utils)
  
On a system with a working mythfrontend, mythrip should run out of the
box.

To run mythrip from the unpacked distributed tarball, run:

   $ ./mythrip

To install mythrip, run (as root):

   # python setup.py install

..and start it with:

   $ mythrip   
